Melton H. HENDERSON and Charles L. Sharitz v. Roy C. TERRILL. No. 6568. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Oct. 5, 1960. A. O. Kiesow, Kansas City, Kan., for appellants. Williamson, Cubbison & Vaughan, Kansas City, Kan., for appellee.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Docketed and dismissed on motion of appellee.
